ets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b66dddc0571c2e82da000621f372799d145e197","tid":358133,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T01:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平凡職業造就世界最強<br />\n武藝精研百餘年，轉世成精靈重拾武者修行<br />\n勇者的師傅大人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無職轉生 到了異世界就拿出真本事</span><br />\n關於我轉生後成為史萊姆的那件事 <br />\n在地下城尋求邂逅是否搞錯了什麽<br />\n為了女兒，我說不定連魔王都能幹掉<br />\n從零開始的魔法書<br />\n<br />\n紅色可以睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左勇者的師傅大人 我套套都有睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n師傅大人個套 好似出得好慢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw <br />\n轉生成史萊姆的那件事<br />\n異世界狂想曲<br />\n哥布林殺手"},{"pid":"1f6e5c67f081cf9520581a37f92d846a78e8b454","tid":358133,"uid":12289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T01:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw例牌<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">愛書的下剋上</span><br />\n謙虛踏實的生活下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢套聽講最後換左cp 係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a966756b5a11f20994698312c919d4341d64f33","tid":358133,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T01:41:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>btw例牌<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">愛書的下剋上</span><br />\n謙虛踏實的生活下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢套聽講最後換左cp 係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢套開始果陣個青梅真係好有男主感覺<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">結果第3章開始就變路人</span>"},{"pid":"3a5a89ca8889726169699fce7e12a53cb60b7144","tid":358133,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T01:42:15.000Z","msg":"涼宮春日<br />\n狼與辛香料<br />\n全金屬狂潮"},{"pid":"b01f3d02dfcd06c238118f7e7bc4b3bdc6297254","tid":358133,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T01:44:41.000